      "raw_text": "President Howard Elliott and\nGeneral Manager Horn Of the\nNorthern Pacific were in Spokane\nthis morning. They made an In\nspection of the work being done\nat Yardley, where 1t Is expected\nthe company will remove the shops.\nThe officials left this afternoon for\nthe South, where they will inspect\nthe building of the road along the\nnorth bank of the Columbia."
